{"tid":1931401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高院判七日內交港鐵831 cctv！","createTime":"2020-03-18T06:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T07:16:56.000Z","uid":50791,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"03b1f0ce4df8287e3f5dcef6cb4d3006a3bb927c","tid":1931401,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"警方8.31在港鐵太子站執法惹爭議，香港教育大學學生會會長梁耀霆自言路經該站時，遭警方無理襲擊及拘捕。為了向警方索償，梁早前入稟法庭申請「第三方披露令」，要求港鐵提供太子站及荔枝角站的閉路電視錄影片段作證據。法官早前聽取陳詞，下令港鐵須安全保管有關片段，今日再頒下判詞，判梁耀霆勝訴，下令港鐵於七日內交出相關的閉路電視錄影片段。<br />\n<br />\n下面比返credit蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200318&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60727168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200318%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60727168&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=c8b008fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200318%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60727168&h=47b4769d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200318&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60727168</a><br />\n<br />\n突然咁好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係中立官定已經拍好晒片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce30f788a90b286e2ffd4b3f592cd8f39fcfdf03","tid":1931401,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"個官想變浮屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d1c783392c5a144979c1f8b072c78440a7a327dd","tid":1931401,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"定係港鐵有新借口"},{"pid":"02b7945c2049b765642779e82d8a442890b6ad84","tid":1931401,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ac7e23298be0758f3bcea25581a1d5a223291f","tid":1931401,"uid":22157